況下為一周。居於青衣的第12名確診病人在本月22日發病、出現咳嗽和氣促前的一周內都在香港，主要在附近街市或住所樓下活動；曾一同吃團年飯的家人和親戚亦無去過湖北的紀錄，顯示病人可能屬本地感染個案。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君稱這代表本港社區內，可能已有病徵輕微、甚至無病徵的人在傳播病毒。她說，希望該病人的個案只是個別情況，但若出現愈來愈多同類個案，就代表新型冠狀病毒可能已出現本地或廣泛傳播，現時當局盡量把所有確診個案及他們的密切接觸者隔離，拖慢或阻止此情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200201/s00001/1580547248016/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%b1%85%e9%9d%92%e8%a1%a3%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba%e8%80%85%e5%80%98%e8%ad%89%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93-%e9%a1%af%e7%a4%ba%e6%88%96%e5%87%ba%e7%8f%be%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0%e5%bb%a3%e6%b3%9b%e5%82%b3%e6%92%ad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200201%2Fs00001%2F1580547248016%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25b1%2585%25e9%259d%2592%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%2580%2598%25e8%25ad%2589%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%259c%25b0%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593-%25e9%25a1%25af%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e6%2588%2596%25e5%2587%25ba%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e6%25b3%259b%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%2592%25ad&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=1d3b1a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200201%2Fs00001%2F1580547248016%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25b1%2585%25e9%259d%2592%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%2580%2598%25e8%25ad%2589%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%259c%25b0%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593-%25e9%25a1%25af%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e6%2588%2596%25e5%2587%25ba%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e6%25b3%259b%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%2592%25ad&h=87c31ea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200201/s0000